original_title: Starrcast V: The Sessions With Renee Paquette and Bryan Danielson
overview: On July 30th The Sessions with Renee Paquette is coming live to FITE as part of Starrcast V. This is a special episode in which the special guest is the multi-time World Heavyweight Champion Bryan Danielson.
title: Starrcast V: The Sessions With Renee Paquette and Bryan Danielson
